frozen food, so I would throw in a TV dinner,

02:04:36.800 --> 02:04:40.070
and that's how I lived. I've tried

02:04:40.080 --> 02:04:42.310
to cook. I can do the wheat

02:04:42.320 --> 02:04:44.229
berry thing and I taught Paisley;

02:04:44.239 --> 02:04:47.430
I did okay. Then

02:04:50.719 --> 02:04:53.030
she took off with it; it blew wind in her sails and she took off. She's way better

02:04:53.040 --> 02:04:53.830
than me.

02:04:53.840 --> 02:04:54.870
Paisley can cook;

02:04:54.880 --> 02:04:56.870
she's a godsend in so many ways.

02:04:56.880 --> 02:04:58.629
They're

02:04:59.510 --> 02:04:59.520
smart;

02:05:01.360 --> 02:05:02.229
all my kids are smart.

02:05:02.239 --> 02:05:04.470
I always say, 'You're

02:05:04.480 --> 02:05:06.310
the 80 and I don't

02:05:06.320 --> 02:05:07.910
complain about the

02:05:07.910 --> 02:05:07.920
20.'We

02:05:07.920 --> 02:05:10.870
are grateful for the 80 and

02:05:10.880 --> 02:05:12.790
we don't focus on the 20. Cooking? Who

02:05:12.800 --> 02:05:15.589
cares? You're a good wife to me

02:05:15.599 --> 02:05:17.510
and I don't care about how many cupcakes

02:05:17.520 --> 02:05:19.669
you can make me. Let Paisley do it.

02:05:22.000 --> 02:05:23.669
But

02:05:23.679 --> 02:05:25.669
what I was saying was just don't

02:05:25.679 --> 02:05:29.109
underestimate

02:05:29.119 --> 02:05:31.750
how effective you are when you

02:05:31.760 --> 02:05:34.550
are supportive of your spouse.

